reviewText: I too just bought this for The Little Kidnappers.  I think it is one of the best Disney movies ever and gets so little recognition.  I wish Disney would put some of their earlier non-animated moves on blu-ray, Hayley Mills, The Ugly Dachshund, etc.
Wanted the movie "The Little Kidnappers" and ended up with a bonus of 4 others.  Glad to get item.
We bought this for The Little Kidnappers movie with Charlton Heston. The others are an added bonus. We love this movie!
